---
layout: base.njk
title: 為自己抽張卡｜溪水邊 Stream Side
description: 溪水邊 Stream Side 為自己抽張卡 — 一張牌卡，一個當下，讓直覺帶你看見今天需要的那道光。
activeNav: cards
pageToast: true
pageStyle: |
  body { background: var(--rice); }

  /* Share toast */
  .toast {
    position: fixed;
    bottom: 2rem;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(80px);
    background: var(--oak);
    color: var(--rice);
    padding: 0.75rem 1.75rem;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.34,1.56,0.64,1);
    z-index: 999;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .toast.show { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0); }

  /* Fade-in animation */
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(16px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  /* ── Fan Layout ── */
  .card-fan {
    position: relative;
    width: min(240px, 64vw);
    height: min(360px, 54vw + 110px);
    margin: 0 auto 6rem; /* bottom space for arc overflow */
  }

  .fan-card {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0;
    width: 100%; height: 100%;
    cursor: pointer;
    transform-origin: 50% 112%;
    transform: rotate(0deg);
    transition: transform 0.55s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.15, 0.64, 1);
    border-radius: 1.25rem;
    will-change: transform;
  }

  .fan-card.spread {
    transform: rotate(var(--fan-angle, 0deg));
  }

  .fan-card.hovered {
    transform: rotate(var(--fan-angle, 0deg)) translateY(-22px);
    transition: transform 0.18s ease-out;
    z-index: 20;
  }

  .fan-card.collapsing {
    transform: rotate(0deg);
    transition: transform 0.38s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
  }

  .fan-card-back {
    width: 100%; height: 100%;
    border-radius: 1.25rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--oak) 0%, #6b4f45 50%, var(--bark) 100%);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--rice);
    position: relative;
    box-shadow: 0 16px 48px rgba(140,106,93,0.22);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .fan-card-back::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 10px;
    border: 1.5px solid rgba(250,243,224,0.22);
    border-radius: 0.85rem;
  }

  .fan-card-back .card-pattern {
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    opacity: 0.45;
  }

  /* Result card — hidden until a fan card is clicked */
  #cardResultWrap {
    display: none;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

pageScript: |
  <script>
    // ── Card data ──
    const CARDS = [
      {
        number: 'No. 01', emoji: '🌊', title: '流動', keyword: '放手 · 信任 · 流動',
        interpretTitle: '流動之卡',
        interpretBody: '今天，也許有什麼事情讓你緊握著不放。這張卡輕輕地問你：如果你願意放手，生命會帶你流向哪裡？\n\n流動不是失去控制，而是相信自己有能力在任何水流中找到方向。讓那些抓太緊的地方，稍微鬆開一點。',
        interpretMessage: '水往低處流，心往溫暖處去。'
      },
      {
        number: 'No. 02', emoji: '🌱', title: '萌芽', keyword: '開始 · 潛力 · 耐心',
        interpretTitle: '萌芽之卡',
        interpretBody: '每一個開始都很小，就像種子破土之前，沒有人看得見它的力量。\n\n你現在正在做的事，或許還沒有成果，但種子已經在土裡了。給它時間，給它光，給它你的耐心。',
        interpretMessage: '最深的根，長出最高的樹。'
      },
      {
        number: 'No. 03', emoji: '☀️', title: '溫暖', keyword: '愛 · 接納 · 當下',
        interpretTitle: '溫暖之卡',
        interpretBody: '有時候，我們最需要的不是解答，而是一個溫暖的所在。\n\n今天，讓這張卡提醒你：你值得被溫柔對待，包括被你自己。把那一點點溫度，先給自己。',
        interpretMessage: '你就是你最需要的那個家。'
      },
      {
        number: 'No. 04', emoji: '🌙', title: '靜默', keyword: '休息 · 內省 · 夜晚',
        interpretTitle: '靜默之卡',
        interpretBody: '在這個總是要求產出的世界裡，靜默是一種勇敢。\n\n今天，也許你不需要解決什麼，也不需要說什麼。只是坐著，讓自己的內心說話，然後聽。',
        interpretMessage: '靜下來，才能聽見自己。'
      },
      {
        number: 'No. 05', emoji: '🦋', title: '轉化', keyword: '改變 · 蛻變 · 勇氣',
        interpretTitle: '轉化之卡',
        interpretBody: '蝴蝶在蛹裡的時候，並不知道自己會飛。它只是經歷著那段黑暗、混沌、看似沒有出口的過程。\n\n也許你正在某個蛹裡。請相信，那不是終點，而是轉化正在發生。',
        interpretMessage: '改變的前一刻，總是最難熬的。'
      },
      {
        number: 'No. 06', emoji: '🌸', title: '綻放', keyword: '展現 · 自信 · 美麗',
        interpretTitle: '綻放之卡',
        interpretBody: '你有些美好的東西，還藏在心裡沒有拿出來。\n\n這張卡問你：是什麼讓你不敢展現真實的自己？那些阻礙，是真實的牆，還是你為自己建造的？今天，試著讓那朵花開一點點。',
        interpretMessage: '你的光，世界需要看見。'
      },
      {
        number: 'No. 07', emoji: '🪨', title: '紮根', keyword: '穩定 · 基礎 · 歸屬',
        interpretTitle: '紮根之卡',
        interpretBody: '當一切都在晃動的時候，找到你的根。\n\n那可能是一個人、一個地方、一段回憶、一種信念。回到它，讓自己在那裡站穩。從穩定的地方，你才能往任何方向生長。',
        interpretMessage: '根越深，風吹時越不怕。'
      },
      {
        number: 'No. 08', emoji: '🕊️', title: '釋放', keyword: '原諒 · 放下 · 自由',
        interpretTitle: '釋放之卡',
        interpretBody: '你是否有什麼事情、什麼情緒，攜帶了很久，卻還沒找到地方放下？\n\n釋放不一定是原諒，也不一定是遺忘。它可以只是決定：「我不讓它繼續佔據我的心了。」今天，找一個小小的釋放。',
        interpretMessage: '放下，是給自己的禮物。'
      }
    ];

    // Spread angles for 10 fan positions (-36° to +36°)
    const FAN_ANGLES = [-36, -27, -19, -12, -5, 5, 12, 19, 27, 36];
    let fanState = 'fan'; // 'fan' | 'collapsing' | 'result'
    let selectedCardIndex = -1;

    function buildFan() {
      const fan = document.getElementById('cardFan');
      fan.innerHTML = '';
      FAN_ANGLES.forEach((angle, i) => {
        const el = document.createElement('div');
        el.className = 'fan-card';
        el.style.setProperty('--fan-angle', angle + 'deg');
        el.setAttribute('role', 'button');
        el.setAttribute('tabindex', '0');
        el.setAttribute('aria-label', '翻牌 ' + (i + 1));
        el.innerHTML = '<div class="fan-card-back"><span class="card-pattern" aria-hidden="true">✦</span></div>';

        el.addEventListener('mouseenter', () => {
          if (fanState !== 'fan') return;
          el.classList.add('hovered');
        });
        el.addEventListener('mouseleave', () => el.classList.remove('hovered'));
        el.addEventListener('click', () => { if (fanState === 'fan') pickCard(); });
        el.addEventListener('keydown', e => {
          if ((e.key === 'Enter' || e.key === ' ') && fanState === 'fan') pickCard();
        });

        fan.appendChild(el);
      });
    }

    function showFan() {
      fanState = 'fan';
      selectedCardIndex = -1;
      document.getElementById('cardFan').style.display = '';
      document.getElementById('cardResultWrap').style.display = 'none';
      document.getElementById('card3d').classList.remove('flipped');
      document.getElementById('interpretation').classList.remove('visible');

      // Trigger spread animation after paint
      requestAnimationFrame(() => requestAnimationFrame(() => {
        document.querySelectorAll('.fan-card').forEach(c => c.classList.add('spread'));
      }));
    }

    function pickCard() {
      if (fanState !== 'fan') return;
      fanState = 'collapsing';

      // Collapse all fan cards to center
      document.querySelectorAll('.fan-card').forEach(c => {
        c.classList.remove('hovered', 'spread');
        c.classList.add('collapsing');
      });

      // Choose a random card from deck
      selectedCardIndex = Math.floor(Math.random() * CARDS.length);

      // After collapse animation → show result card
      setTimeout(() => {
        document.getElementById('cardFan').style.display = 'none';

        const card = CARDS[selectedCardIndex];
        document.getElementById('cardNumber').textContent = card.number;
        document.getElementById('cardEmoji').textContent = card.emoji;
        document.getElementById('cardTitle').textContent = card.title;
        document.getElementById('cardKeyword').textContent = card.keyword;
        document.getElementById('interpretTitle').textContent = card.interpretTitle;
        document.getElementById('interpretBody').textContent = card.interpretBody;
        document.getElementById('interpretMessage').textContent = '「' + card.interpretMessage + '」';

        document.getElementById('cardResultWrap').style.display = 'block';

        // Flip the result card — small delay ensures reflow before transition starts
        setTimeout(() => {
          document.getElementById('card3d').classList.add('flipped');
          fanState = 'result';

          setTimeout(() => {
            const interp = document.getElementById('interpretation');
            interp.classList.add('visible');
            interp.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'nearest' });
          }, 650);
        }, 40);
      }, 450);
    }

    function redraw() {
      if (fanState === 'result') {
        document.getElementById('card3d').classList.remove('flipped');
        document.getElementById('interpretation').classList.remove('visible');
        setTimeout(() => { buildFan(); showFan(); }, 420);
      } else {
        buildFan();
        showFan();
      }
    }

    function shareCard() {
      const card = selectedCardIndex >= 0 ? CARDS[selectedCardIndex] : null;
      const text = card
        ? '我從溪水邊抽到了「' + card.title + '」' + card.emoji + '\n' + card.interpretMessage + '\n\n溪水邊 Stream Side · 為自己抽張卡'
        : '我正在溪水邊為自己抽張卡 🃏\n溪水邊 Stream Side';
      if (navigator.share) {
        navigator.share({ title: '溪水邊 · 為自己抽張卡', text, url: window.location.href })
          .catch(() => copyToClipboard(text));
      } else {
        copyToClipboard(text);
      }
    }

    function copyToClipboard(text) {
      navigator.clipboard.writeText(text + '\n' + window.location.href)
        .then(() => showToast('✓ 已複製到剪貼板'))
        .catch(() => showToast('請手動複製頁面連結分享'));
    }

    function showToast(msg) {
      const toast = document.getElementById('toast');
      toast.textContent = msg;
      toast.classList.add('show');
      setTimeout(() => toast.classList.remove('show'), 2800);
    }

    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
      buildFan();
      showFan();
    });
  </script>
---

<!-- ══════════════ PAGE INTRO ══════════════ -->
<div style="text-align:center;padding:4rem 1.5rem 1rem;">
  <p style="font-size:0.8rem;letter-spacing:0.18em;color:var(--straw);margin-bottom:0.5rem;text-transform:uppercase;">Card Reading</p>
  <h1 style="font-size:clamp(1.8rem,3.5vw,2.5rem);color:var(--oak);margin-bottom:0.75rem;">為自己抽張卡</h1>
  <p style="color:rgba(67,52,48,0.6);font-size:0.95rem;max-width:420px;margin:0 auto;line-height:1.9;">
    深呼吸，靜下心來，<br>
    點擊任意一張牌，翻開今天最需要看見的那道光。
  </p>
</div>

<!-- ══════════════ CARD STAGE ══════════════ -->
<section class="card-stage" aria-labelledby="card-heading">
  <h2 id="card-heading" style="position:absolute;opacity:0;pointer-events:none;">互動抽卡區</h2>

  <!-- Fan of 10 cards (populated by JS) -->
  <div class="card-fan" id="cardFan" aria-label="牌卡組，點擊任一張翻牌"></div>

  <!-- Result card — shown after fan collapses -->
  <div class="card-3d-wrap" id="cardResultWrap">
    <div class="card-3d" id="card3d">

      <!-- Back face -->
      <div class="card-face card-back-face" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="card-pattern">✦</div>
      </div>

      <!-- Front face -->
      <div class="card-face card-front-face" id="cardFront">
        <p class="card-number" id="cardNumber">No. —</p>
        <div class="card-image-area" id="cardEmoji" aria-hidden="true">✨</div>
        <h3 id="cardTitle"></h3>
        <p id="cardKeyword" style="font-size:0.78rem;color:var(--straw);font-weight:600;margin:0.2rem 0 0.4rem;"></p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ── Control Buttons ── -->
  <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:2.5rem;" role="group" aria-label="抽卡操作">
    <button class="btn-primary" id="redrawBtn" onclick="redraw()" aria-label="重新抽卡" style="font-size:0.85rem;padding:0.6rem 1.5rem;">
      ✦ 重新抽卡
    </button>
    <button class="btn-outline" id="shareBtn" onclick="shareCard()" aria-label="分享牌卡" style="font-size:0.85rem;padding:0.6rem 1.5rem;">
      ↗ 分享
    </button>
  </div>

  <!-- ── Interpretation Area ── -->
  <div class="card-interpretation" id="interpretation" role="region" aria-live="polite" aria-label="牌卡解析">
    <div style="width:40px;height:2px;background:var(--straw);margin:0 auto 1.5rem;border-radius:2px;"></div>
    <h2 id="interpretTitle"></h2>
    <p id="interpretBody" style="margin-top:0.75rem;white-space:pre-line;"></p>
    <p class="card-message" id="interpretMessage"></p>
    <div style="margin-top:2rem;display:flex;gap:0.75rem;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <button onclick="shareCard()" class="btn-outline" style="font-size:0.82rem;padding:0.5rem 1.4rem;">分享這張卡</button>
      <a href="{{ '/articles/' | url }}" class="btn-outline" style="font-size:0.82rem;padding:0.5rem 1.4rem;">閱讀相關文章</a>
    </div>
  </div>

</section>

<!-- ══════════════ HOW TO USE ══════════════ -->
